<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lose-v">lose <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /luːz/    美 /luːz/  </p>
<p>(lost, lost)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>失去；丢失；丧失：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He lost his wallet yesterday when he was in a crowded bus. 
昨天他在拥挤的公交车上丢失了钱包。</p><footer>北师大④ – 10</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Having lost his father, Roy became very unhappy.
失去了父亲，罗伊非常忧伤。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>lose confidence / interest / hope</strong> 
失去信心/兴趣/希望</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If he had followed my advice, he wouldn’t have <strong>lost</strong> his <strong>job</strong>.
他要是听从了我的劝告，就不会丢掉工作。</p><footer>2010 湖南</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>迷失；使迷路：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>lost my way</strong> in the network of tiny alleys.
我在纵横交错的小巷子里迷了路。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>输掉</strong></h4>
<p>反 win： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our team lost the match so we were very disappointed.
我们队输掉了比赛，我们很失望。</p><footer>外研① – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Argentina <strong>lost to</strong> German in the 2014 FIFA World Cup.
在2014年世界杯足球赛上，阿根廷队败给了德国队。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(使) 亏损；(使) 损失：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company lost heavily because of wrong judgment.
因为判断失误，公司损失惨重。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>错过；浪费：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I lost the last sentence of his speech. 
我没听到他演讲的最后一句话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Come on, <strong>there’s no time to lose</strong>. 
快点儿，没时间磨蹭了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="lose-oneself-in">lose oneself in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>专心于；全神贯注于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She listened attentively to the music, losing herself in its beauty. 
她专注地听着音乐，完全沉浸在美妙的旋律之中。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>loser /'luːzə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>